data.description: Back on the market! BEAUTIFUL BRICK 4/2 home in Cantonment offers quiet peaceful living, within easy distance of the interstate and business district of Nine-Mile Rd. This very functional split-floor plan boasts over 2500 sqft. of fresh paint and numerous special touches such as NEW WOOD-LOOK FLOORING and a GORGEOUS SHIP-LAP WALL and custom window casings. The  bright and open entry-way is flanked by a formal dining room and a potential family room or home office space. STAINLESS STEEL appliances and TONS of counter space, help you serve up meals for friends and family with plenty of elbow-room in the eat-in Kitchen AND Breakfast bar adjacent to the spacious Living Room. Gather around the Gas FIREPLACE on those cool NW Florida evenings or enjoy time out on the private & open back porch, overlooking the woods and a nearby pond. The Master Bedroom is a generously-sized space perfect for some R&R, where you can enjoy the garden tub, separate shower and dual-vanity. All additional bedrooms are carpeted and have ceiling fans and roomy closets - room for everyone! The quiet neighborhood, well-kept landscaping with full front and back SPRINKLER system and great curb appeal will make you happy to come home! Move-in ready and priced right, this one wonât last long! Schedule your showing today! (Buyer was unable to proceed with purchase due to financing.)
